belongs_to_collection.name: Active Duty's Battle of the Bottoms Series

overview: When Chase Tyler talks about his time in the National Guard, things start to get hot and heavy between him and Nick Clay. So watch as these two studs go all out. Andrew Miller and Jay Tee fuck long and hard. Cody Kodak is having trouble fitting in at the military. But Jon Campanelli is here to teach Cody all the tricks to fitting in. The chemistry between Brandon Anderson and new recruit Noah Quinn is undeniable, so watch as these two studs have at it in Battle of the Bottoms 15.
title: Battle of the Bottoms 15
